[[/module]]
[[collapsible show="Mr Flagg's Wild Ride (Commentary)" hide="-Close"]]
My first SCP! This was born from a love of the edutainment youtube genre, with special thanks to the channel 'Explosions + Fire', and qntm's antimemetics. Like a reoccurring theme I've found writing these commentaries, I'm not really satisfied with the ending, but this was a blast to write and explore.

The idea in this one was to try and represent burnout. Flagg's breakdown isn't supposed to be because of anything memetic, it's just the natural progression when you're working with objects you forget for long, long shifts. Idk how well that came through, but people seemed to enjoy it regardless, as it's currently my most successful thing.[[span class="fnnum"]].[[/span]][[span class="fncon"]]Technically my 7 word entry to 'I, hub' puts that above this. I've decided not to put that on my author page for some reason.[[/span]]
[[/collapsible]]
------------
* [[[SCP-4536 | SCP-4536 - The Great American Pyramid]]]
[[module ListPages name="scp-4536" category="*" order="created_at desc" limit="1" separate="no"]]
