* [[[operation-lahmi-gath | Emergency Alteration of Operation Lahmi-Gath]]]
[[module ListPages name="operation-lahmi-gath" category="*" order="created_at desc" limit="1" separate="no"]]
(%%created_at%%) (+%%rating%%), Last comment by %%commented_by%%, %%commented_at%%
[[/module]]
[[collapsible show="A 5000 word rant about Americans (Commentary)" hide="-Close"]]
This was my first entry onto the site, and incidentally also my longest by like 3000 words. I've always been mildly irritated by how America-centric the Foundation is, and this is my thesis on why that's a bad idea. It was one hell of a difficult thing to balance non-partisanship, intrigue, detail and keep it Foundation focused, but I think it came out pretty good. I'm not that happy with the ending and would probably do it differently with hindsight, but it was a fun first foray onto the site :)

I'd really like to write more about the Foundation in this world. There's certainly more to write, so stay tuned?
[[/collapsible]]
